parameters:
Cerburus Octopus: I'll challenge you again and take over
this organization... But until you defeat Dynamite Abalone
and unify the city, I'll work for you as a lowly
underling... Hmph...

Memimi: Ah, I look forward to your revenge! But in the end,
I will win again! Hahaha...

Cerburus Octopus: Tch... Acting all high and mighty... Even
after being forced to wear erotic outfits and being made to
do reverse rape on a TV talent show, you're still so
cocky...

Memimi: Could you not bring that up so much? It bothers me
quite a bit...

Cerburus Octopus: That mayor has caused trouble for almost
every monster in Doritoku City... This isn't just your
problem or Shark Broccoli's anymore!! The entire city's
monsters are pinning their hopes on the match with the Shark
Duke!!

Memimi: Of course I understand... The responsibility is
immense. If we defeat him, the cause of this dark age... it
will undoubtedly be a huge step towards our long-cherished
wish!

Cerburus Octopus: Even my family's boxing gym wouldn't have
suffered from the recession if it weren't for him... At the
very least, you've got to punch him for me too. Listen, I'll
teach you a boxer's punch... with a one-two... come on!

Cerburus Octopus: Cough... Keep it up like that in the real
deal... gah...

Memimi unleashed her inner ferocity, significantly boosting
her attack power...

Underling: When I joined the organization, I never thought
we could unify the city, but thanks to Lord Shark's
achievements, it's starting to feel like a reality. If you
never forget hope, anything can happen.

Memimi: Never give up on your dreams... I will continue to
fight as many times as it takes to achieve my goal. You all
should just believe in me and Lord Shark Broccoli, and
follow us relentlessly...

Underling: (Above all, seeing Lord Shark's various erotic
forms was like a dream come true... The camera in the shower
room has been removed, but I've saved recordings for days
and watched them over and over... I know it's wrong, but
there's no way I can delete the data...)

Memimi: It seems you're trembling with emotion... you've
gone silent...

Underling: To think the mayor would show up... I never
imagined it! That bastard, strutting around so
shamelessly...! And if we lose, Lord Shark Broccoli making
an AV debut of all things!! I really want to see it, but the
nerve of him...!
Memimi: Did I let a bit of my true feelings slip...? Hey...

Underling: This... is a personal gift from me! I bought it
with my own money... "Delicious Powder," please eat it!! As
someone involved in the powder refining business, no matter
what happens, I can't let the manufacturing method be passed
on...

Memimi: Thank you... I also want to protect the Delicious
Powder. Lord Shark Broccoli's greatest masterpiece, this
powder, I won't hand it over to anyone...

Eating the nutrient-packed powder gave a boost of energy!
Max HP increased by 50!

Memimi: Boss Shark Broccoli... Our long-cherished goal of
unifying all the organizations in the city is just one
victory away. I will make it happen, even if it costs me my
life... Please look forward to it!

Shark Broccoli: Duke Shark... You have truly done well. You
are my pride and joy...

Shark Broccoli: However, you tend to take on everything by
yourself... It's not just about Monster Fights... No, in
fact, unifying all the organizations in the city is not the
only path to peace. Sometimes it's important to rely on
those around you and think flexibly about the future...

Memimi: ...You may be right... But, Boss... It's just my
nature, and there's nothing I can do about it...

Shark Broccoli: ...The root of your inability to rely on
others probably stems from the trauma of when the orphanage
you grew up in from a young age was shut down, and no one
was there to help you...

Memimi: It was a terrible incident... Suddenly thrown out of
the orphanage with the other kids, and I, being the oldest,
felt such despair...

Memimi: Without access to the internet or a phone, unable to
rely on anyone, I struggled so much to find homes for
everyone... Betrayed and abandoned by so many... In the end,
I was left alone... Exhausted and unable to move...

Memimi: In the end, it was only you, Boss Shark Broccoli,
who helped me... Now I have comrades and many people I can
trust. But deep down... There's a part of me that can't
entrust important things to others...

Shark Broccoli: Time will eventually heal... But until
then... Please don't overdo it... We will also help you with
all our might...

Shark Broccoli: ...I too have faced a great setback in the
past... Left without help, without a place to belong...
Betrayed by comrades... Dumped by a woman...

Shark Broccoli: There's not a night I don't regret that
day... But now, I'm truly grateful for everyone in the
organization. To achieve peace in the city, what I can do
alone is far too little...

Memimi: Boss, you are a wonderful person... Everyone here
has been saved by Boss Shark Broccoli, in one way or
another. That's why we work as your hands and feet.

Shark Broccoli: Thank you... But the truth is... I'm not
really qualified to stand above everyone. When the city of
Doritoku becomes peaceful, I'll reveal everything... And
then, there will be no place for me here...

Memimi: No matter what your past may be, there is no doubt
that Boss Shark Broccoli is a wonderful person!! Please
don't say such sad things...! No matter what we hear, we
will not forget the kindness we have received!!

Shark Broccoli: ...I'm sorry for making you anxious before
the match, Duke Shark... Let's leave this conversation here
for now. But remember, on that day, I made a vow...

Shark Broccoli: To return this asparagus to its rightful
place and atone for the sins we have committed...!
Memimi: Aspara... Huh? What were we talking about again...?

Shark Broccoli: I'm sorry, Duke Shark... We've burdened you
with the negative legacy we caused... Mayor Orca, Orca
Asparagus was a junior in the wrestling organization I used
to belong to.

Memimi: I believe in you, Boss Shark Broccoli. No matter
what happened in the past, I know that you have always been
dedicated to everyone in the dark organization...

Shark Broccoli: Thank you, Duke Shark... It all started on
that day... It was because of my wrong judgment that
everything happened... That day... when it all began...

Underling: Was it three years ago that Lord Shark Broccoli
was picked up by the big boss? This organization was formed
five years ago, and back then, Monster Fight didn't even
exist yet...

Memimi: I've heard that Monster Fight started about two
years ago. The big boss initially didn't intend to bring me
into the dark organization, so I'm not very familiar with
what happened at that time... I joined the organization a
year ago, and my debut in Monster Fight was half a year ago.

Underling: That's a rapid rise... Now Lord Shark Broccoli
has become one of the most important figures in the dark
organization, on the verge of unifying the city... Seriously
amazing...

Memimi: The one I need to repay isn't just Lord Shark
Broccoli... It's also everyone in the organization who has
walked with me and sometimes guided me. I truly am grateful
to all the people around me...

Underling: You don't have to worry about that...! Just being
able to see you in erotic outfits and being allowed to
fondle your breasts is more than I could ever ask for...!

Memimi: That wasn't meant as a show of gratitude...! You...
exposing my shame to close acquaintances... My relationships
are... ugh...

Underling: Lord Shark... if Shark Broccoli-san loses and has
to make an AV debut...! I absolutely hate that idea... I
want Shark Broccoli-san to be mine alone... I do want to see
Shark Broccoli-san having sex, but I don't want her to do it
with anyone other than me...!!

Memimi: Calm down... that's disgusting!! Stop repeating
'sex' over and over!!

Underling: But even if you say that... just watching her on
TV forcefully having her way with celebrities, I felt like I
was going to lose it, and now to think she has to sleep
around with other men as a routine... it does give me a bit
of a hard-on, but...

Memimi: ...Seriously, just shut up... I get how you feel,
but...

Underling: At least, take this...! It's a heart-shaped
necklace that I chose!! Please wear it and defeat Mayor
Orca...!!

Memimi: That's creepy... no, I mean... uh, I'll just accept
the sentiment... thank you...

With the underling's feelings received, Memimi's attack
power increased slightly...

Anomalocaris: The next Monster Fight will determine who
unifies the city's dark organizations... It's so
thrilling... I really wanted to be the one to achieve it...
but I have to acknowledge your strength...

Memimi: Hehe, you've become quite honest, haven't you,
Anomalocaris... Just watch, I will surely defeat the final
formidable enemy and present the throne of Dorieto City to
Lord Shark Broccoli!

Anomalocaris: Even after making you do a naked masturbation
run around the city, you didn't break and managed to get
your revenge, staying loyal to the boss... Maybe someone
like you is a true monster...

Memimi: Forget about that story... damn it... When you're a
monster at my level, such episodes are nothing to boast
about, they're just embarrassing to talk about... damn,
damn...

Anomalocaris: I remember... it was five years ago... I had
just graduated high school, had my job lined up, and was
enjoying my spring break... but as soon as the mayor
changed, the company went under, and before the entrance
ceremony, I was decided unemployed...

Memimi: What a heartbreaking episode... Everyone who joins a
dark organization has their life go awry somewhere, and when
they can't take it anymore, they stray from their path...

Anomalocaris: Please... make him realize it for me too...!
My family runs a karate dojo... I'll teach you a move! Like
this... make your legs into an inverted 'V', and then,
tighten like this...

Anomalocaris: Hmm... with this, even if a runaway train
comes barreling in, you'll be able to withstand it! I'm
counting on you... do your best...!

Memimi: I think a runaway express train is a bit much... but
this technique will be useful. Thank you, Anomalocaris...
Memimi's defense has greatly increased! Max HP up by 300!

Underling: It seems Cerberus Octopus-sama has acknowledged
you and the big boss as his superiors... He'll never admit
it out loud, though. We, the former minions of Cerberus
Octopus, will also cooperate with all our might towards the
unification of the city.

Memimi: That's reassuring... With the merger of our
organization and the Cerberus Octopus faction, we now have
over 100 members. Moreover, smaller organizations are
rushing to join us to secure good positions while they can.
In terms of numbers alone, we're already the largest force
in the city...

Underling: It's all thanks to us for spreading those videos
of Shark Duke all over the city in advance! That's what
explosively increased the city's attention...

Memimi: ...You've done something unnecessary... I really
wanted to collect all the distributed DVDs, but it's too
late now... They've been copied far more than they were
sold, and have spread even outside the city...

Underling: It's been 5 years since the Orca Mayor took
office... His misrule continues, and the people who have
somehow endured are reaching their limit. For now, the
majority of citizens can still lead decent lives, but who
knows how long that will last...

Memimi: The chain of tragedies must be stopped here... He is
the worst monster spawned by this city of Dorie. If I don't
defeat him now, a future of ruin awaits all the citizens...

Underling: I used to be a subordinate of Lord Anomalocaris,
but now that I'm under you, I truly think it was the right
decision. If the city's underworld organizations are unified
and the conflicts cease, society should become better...

Memimi: The dark organizations are full of people with no
money, no education, and no jobs, but if everyone comes
together as one, what we can do will increase dramatically.
We also need to think about various things for the city
after unification...

Underling: What exactly are you planning to do...? Even if
the city becomes peaceful, can you really live a decent life
after spreading uncensored masturbation videos all over the
world as the cost of victory...?

Memimi: At this point in time, I'm living quite normally,
you know? Just because people point fingers at me on the
street or I see my genitals all over the internet... it
doesn't change my life, does it?

Underling: I remember... Right after the current mayor took
office, taxes skyrocketed... Road maintenance and public
services were drastically cut back. Many facilities were
closed, and a lot of stores were forced out by land
sharks...

Memimi: With the rise in unemployment, numerous dark
organizations and monsters emerged, marking the start of
Doritoku City's dark age... I never imagined the day would
come when we'd fight the mayor who's the root of all this.

Underling: That mayor rarely makes public appearances, so
hardly anyone has seen him. I never would have guessed he
was a monster...

Memimi: First of all, is it even possible to just replace a
mayor by defeating him? I really don't understand the world
of politics...

Memimi: *pant* *pant*... That was an interesting movie...!
As expected of Shark Broccoli Boss's choice!! I've devised a
technique as tumultuous as a storm!!
